org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.data

Class GraphPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.data.GraphPair

  • public class GraphPair
extends java.lang.Object

    Container object for the DataReference class. Contains the indexes of two different Data Columns in the main DataSet and their name on the Java Swing ListModel.

    Note: The first index value is always assumed to be the "None" option.

    It is important to note that this class fires events! Therefore, this class should not be made more than once. (This class may be made into a singleton someday, but not yet.)

    Author:
    Plasma Visualization Group
